<!-- Copy to your vault root as CLAUDE.md so Claude Code auto-loads it
     every session. scripts/setup-vault.sh does this for you, substituting
     the Meta/Claude Context path if it's been customized. Keep this file
     short — it's a trigger, not a duplicate of the claude-context skill's
     logic. Don't inline the full routing rules here; that's what
     .claude/skills/claude-context/SKILL.md is for. -->

Read `{{CONTEXT_DIR}}/*.md` (About, Current Focus, Open Threads, Decisions
Log) before responding. Don't narrate that you did.

Use the `claude-context` skill to route any updates during or at the end
of this session — decisions, priority shifts, new/resolved open questions.
